因應[[工党_(英国)|工黨]]在{{tsl|en|2006 United Kingdom local elections|2006年英國地方選舉}}表現惡劣，[[英國首相|英國首相]][[托尼·布莱尔|托尼·布莱尔]]在選舉翌日，即5月5日[[內閣改組|改組]][[第三次貝理雅內閣|他的第三次內閣]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Her Majesty s Cabinet and Ministerial list|url=http://www.number10.gov.uk/output/Page9393.asp|date=2006-05-05|publisher=英國政府|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060616125549/http://www.number10.gov.uk/output/Page9393.asp|archivedate=2006-06-16|accessdate=2020-10-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，也是他任內最大規模的一次<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|title=Clarke is fired in Cabinet purge|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/4975938.stm|date=2006-05-05|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102000159/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/4975938.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自2001年起出任外交大臣並主力負責[[反恐战争|反恐战争]]的[[施仲宏|施仲宏]]，在內閣改組後轉任下議院領袖兼掌璽大臣，令外界始料不及<ref>{{Cite news|title=Foreign doubts after Straw's exit|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/4979674.stm|date=2006-05-06|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101125138/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/4979674.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一方認為他處理內外政已經十年，因而主動要求退出幕前<ref name=":0">{{cite news|url=http://politics.guardian.co.uk/labour/story/0,,1768251,00.html|title=Clarke sacked in major cabinet reshuffle|newspaper=衛報|accessdate=2013-05-24|location=倫敦|date=2006-05-09|last=King|first=Oliver|archive-date=2006-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060517214624/http://politics.guardian.co.uk/labour/story/0,,1768251,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；另一方則認為施氏與白高敦走得越來越接近，而且反對向伊朗發動軍事行動，令貝理雅感到不滿<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|title=PM rubbishes Straw axing claims|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/4750397.stm|date=2006-05-08|accessdate=2020-10-30|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106232018/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/4750397.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過貝相表明後者的猜測純屬「垃圾」<ref name=":2" />。最終，[[玛格丽特·贝克特|玛格丽特·贝克特]]成為首位女性外交大臣，而施仲宏接任下議院領袖和掌璽大臣<ref name=":0" />。原本由{{tsl|en|Secretary of State for Constitutional Affairs|憲制事務大臣}}處理的{{tsl|en|Reform of the House of Lords|改革上議院}}和[[政治献金|政治献金]]問題，則成為施氏的主要任務<ref name=":0" />。至於在改組前出任下院領袖的[[禤智輝|禤智輝]]，則改任[[外交、聯邦及發展事務部|外交部]]新設立的{{tsl|en|Minister of State for Europe|歐洲國務大臣}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Geoff Hoon's Ugandan affair|url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2006/nov/01/hoonsugandandiscussions|accessdate=2020-10-29|date=2006-11-01|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106163923/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2006/nov/01/hoonsugandandiscussions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當禤氏離開首相府時，他一度以為自己留任內閣更升官任「歐洲大臣」，後來才發現是次一級的國務大臣<ref>{{Cite news|title=The Backbencher, Guardian Unlimited's weekly insider's guide to Westminster, explains why Geoff Hoon looked so peeved at PMQs today.|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/nov/01/1|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2006-11-01|accessdate=2020-10-29|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Guardian|last=Staff|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102224843/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/nov/01/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>；雖然續可列席內閣，但因失去內閣表決權，而被視為實際上降職<ref>{{cite news|last=Hinsliff|first=Gaby|url=http://politics.guardian.co.uk/labour/story/0,,1769542,00.html|title=The last throw of the dice|work=The Observer|location=London|date=2006-05-06|accessdate=2017-11-17|archive-date=2007-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070825194444/http://politics.guardian.co.uk/labour/story/0,,1769542,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[英國副首相|副首相]]兼[[首席大臣|首席大臣]][[彭仕國|彭仕國]]被揭發與秘書發生關係後，據報主動放棄副首相辦公室的所有部門職權，即[[住房、社区和地方政府事务部|社區及地方政府事務]]，但決定留任該兩職<ref name=":1" />。至於[[教育大臣|教育及技術大臣]]{{tsl|en|Ruth Kelly|簡樂芙}}則獲委任為首任[[房屋、社區及地方政府事務大臣|社區及地方政府大臣]]{{tsl|en|Ruth Kelly|簡樂芙}}，新部門除了負責原本隸屬副首相的職權外，亦接手{{tsl|en|Department of Trade and Industry (United Kingdom)|貿易及工業部}}的平等事務，以及{{tsl|en|Minister of State for Communities and Local Government|社區及地方政府國務大臣}}[[文禮彬|文禮彬]]的職權<ref name=":1" />。

另外，[[內政大臣_(英國)|內政大臣]]{{tsl|en|Charles Clarke|祈卓禮}}在改組後離開政府，是改組中最高級的人事變動<ref name=":0" />。有報導指，祈氏堅持續任內政大臣處理爛攤子，但被首相拒絕，而他亦因拒絕出任閣僚和初級職位，最終選擇離開政府<ref name=":1" />。

